{"tid":2147093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【新冠肺炎】機動部隊23歲男警初步確診　未知行蹤及感染源頭","createTime":"2020-08-09T04:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T04:25:21.000Z","uid":107470,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"160ed854c3012e1f315ebaadd559bd3d0c1ce753","tid":2147093,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"本港疫情未止，警方指一名駐守機動部隊的23歲男警初步確診病，他於昨日（8日）自行前往指定診所接受病毒檢測，之後收到檢測中心通知其對2019冠狀病毒病呈陽性反應。該名男警正在接受機動部隊訓練，沒有進行與公眾接觸的工作，於過去14日沒有外遊記錄，最後一日上班日為8月7日。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2719108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2719108&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=cec62e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2719108</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790c62888a4e81cdcd97bf8434a9b230c4c240c4","tid":2147093,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"他只是個孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\